abstract: >-
  MorphoScope is a Python-based GUI application for quantifying 
  structural plasticity in neuronal projections from 3D confocal 
  microscopy images. It implements the methodology described in 
  Petsakou et al., 2015 (Cell), providing automated calculation of 
  3D spread metrics, axonal volume, geometric volume, and 
  fluorescence density with PCA-based rotation for objective 
  axis alignment.
